channel.title: Lins Interface Editor Being Weird?
channel.description: I'm using PI Enhanced v3 I believe it is, and the chatbox sprites are really stupid. So I went in with Toms Cache Editor Jarred with unlimited cache size, and replaced it. Note, before this the interface editor was working 100% fine. After it repacked the cache and shit, I went to open it with the editor, and it came up with an error: "Some sprites are missing...". Turns out all sprites are missing and it's just black screen and when you click on it it just shows the configs. I thought I corrupted the image part of the cache, but it opened right back up with the cache editor... :S So yea... Any ideas what might be wrong?
